Title: Microsoft v. Google - The Value of Acquired IP

Author: pg
Content:
It seems a reasonable model to say that outcome = idea x execution, but there's no reason to put the dollar sign on the execution.

Rather than

outcome = idea x $execution

The more honest model would be

outcome = $(idea x execution)
